"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Exchange models have always interested me. With my background in marketplaces, the business model is pretty simple to understand: a take rate on every trade + upcharges on the more “exotic” products & features like derivatives & margin. However, building on chain with a Layer 2 via Starkware is an interesting approach which lends dydx’s comp set to more of a “DeFi Protocol” than an exchange business model like Coinbase. This helps them avoid the headwinds of traditional brokerage/exchanges which are currently racing to the bottom in terms of fees.\\n\\nCombine an already exotic product suite offering by dydx and a governance token that is powering an ecosystem to enable staking, LP mining & discounts/incentives on trades and there’s a formula for powerful ecosystem growth.\\n\\nSign up was insanely easy as well. Just connect your Metamask Wallet, create a user and add your email and enable dydx to approve USDC through your Metamask and there you go. I just wish the whole product suite was available in the US.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/0su4ZL9eLz1YvkytTIClh.jpg?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640826586,\"title\":\"An Overview of dydx\"},\"digest\":\"1KE-s7Ae79BQ9NfmpHeLBTyOX4uW8GaGw7a6T1vCDgY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x23bdEb4396BEB7e179c65A3FcA025EA2ABC156D5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aVF2Lzd_UV9bZDujGuAPM45Vvq4dYAfcjiCUC8P7K3E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"6MH-Y8z6P04Yt1NrUsm8D29XzocPE2P03iS3YxBAYfg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ggFSY3U4wGAqruwnI3FKA4d-2F0sOQImu3BUiyBX3bcxZP_AkNjP2opJ-RTfuJCFPs5y33OXh4YBTfnpBxv5Ww\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5ffa1583845f23b874f93567e9f1b8dcbe471390cdffe45ede5b47248360fbde18cd01eadf2f2288607b9842fb30f9cca7bd20cdffbfeffa46134bf38eab69cc1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\